{"id":422904046,"lang":"cpp","time":"1 year, 7 months","timestamp":1606034382,"status_display":"Wrong Answer","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/422904046/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int myAtoi(string s) {\n        int start;\n        string str;\n        bool sign;\n        long long pro=1;\n        long long sum=0;\n        for(start=0;start<s.size();){\n            if(s[start]!=' ') break;\n            start++;\n        }\n        if(isdigit(s[start])){\n            for(int i=start;i<s.size();i++){\n                if(!isdigit(s[i])) break;\n                str+=s[i];\n            }\n            sign=0;\n        }\n        else if(s[start]=='-'){\n            for(int i=start+1;i<s.size();i++){\n                if(!isdigit(s[i])) break;\n                str+=s[i];\n            }\n            sign=1;\n        }\n        else if(s[start]=='+'){\n            for(int i=start+1;i<s.size();i++){\n                if(!isdigit(s[i])) break;\n                str+=s[i];\n            }\n            sign=0;\n        }\n        else{\n            return 0;\n        }\n        if(str.size()>11){\n            return -2147483648;\n        }\n        for(int i=str.size()-1;i>=0;i--){\n            sum+=pro*(str[i]-'0');\n            pro*=10;\n        }\n        if(sum>2147483647 || -sum<-2147483648){\n            if(sign) return -2147483648;\n            else return 2147483648;\n        }\n        else{\n            if(sign) return -sum;\n            else return sum;\n        }\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi"}
